==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fascicled
<hw>Fas"ci*cled</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Growing in a
bundle, tuft, or close cluster; <as>as, the <ex>fascicled</ex> leaves of
the pine or larch; the <ex>fascicled</ex> roots of the dahlia;
<ex>fascicled</ex> muscle fibers; <ex>fascicled</ex> tufts of
hair.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fascicular</ent>⟦br⟧
